name: Lady Kushinada
skill: Recovers 1243/1583 HP for 3 team members with the lowest HP.

additional_data.description: The spirit of a goddess from Japanese mythology. She lived peacefully as the wife of Susanoo-no-Mikoto, until one day her husband turned into a little girl. She believes he will return to his old self someday and is secrectly determined to protect him.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ "Is this Destiny? -Orochi on the Counterattack-" Event: Defeat LVL 20, 25, 30 Yamata-no-Orochi.
◦ "Is this Destiny? -Orochi on the Counterattack-" Event: Random drops after LVL 20.
additional_data.notes_and_trivia: ◦  Increase damage dealt by 20% while battling Yamata-no-Orochi during the "Is this Destiny? -Orochi on the Counterattack-" event.

main: "Oh, how I adore my little Susanoo!"
summon: "I do this for my beloved Susanoo!"
limit_break: "I'll work extra hard for my little Susanoo!"
